---
title: Easy Malaysian Veggie & Udon Noodle Laksa with Roasted Peanuts & Lemon
description: Laksa is taking centre stage tonight, with Asian veggies as its leading lady. Our version is a take on the Singaporean laksa lemak,
and uses coconut milk and garlic paste to draw out the Asian flavours you know and love.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
